gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Grizzlies 111, Bucks 101
gameRecap.excerpt: The Grizzlies defeated the Bucks, 111-101 after outscoring Milwaukee 32-23 in the 4th. Jaren Jackson Jr. (35 points, three rebounds, four assists) and GG Jackson (15 points, 12 rebounds) led the Grizzlies as Brook Lopez (25 points, 10 rebounds, five 3PM) and Giannis Antetokounmpo (21 points, seven rebounds, eight assists) totaled 46 for the Bucks.
